{"tid":1667993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你既世界唔需要我參與","createTime":"2019-10-21T18:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T22:35:33.000Z","uid":44035,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5609683ec1506f62e23e7021fab099474154fb32","tid":1667993,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:07:40.000Z","msg":"我地就好似兩條平行線咁 平來絕對唔會有交集<br />\n偏偏有意外發生 令兩條線交叉左一下咁多<br />\n最後始終都係會變返兩條線 唔會有結果<br />\n或者應該當搭左架巴士 你咁岩坐係我隔離位<br />\n而呢程巴士到站後 我地都唔會再見<br />\n大家各自有自己既生活 何必勉強？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d3543f74950b9e50c3094aafda1fa45ee3b4f4","tid":1667993,"uid":167178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"本身就唔應該一齊 最後分開都係註定<br />\n你既世界根本就唔需要我"},{"pid":"2684a02f01bda7c2ac5c1a232bacf41ae9f1729a","tid":1667993,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqPgkdq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqPgkdq.jpg&h=f95f797f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjkGwj5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjkGwj5.jpg&h=0e62a97b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctTdnrL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctTdnrL.jpg&h=6f7684c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a26a0eaaaf91afeadc0a23d318fe94c7546ef85d","tid":1667993,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:57:50.000Z","msg":"手足我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa340373c6c383fe19bc60640d030bba2d90ed2","tid":1667993,"uid":305822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da87cccc829c194f9baa27842d69d05b4809e4d8","tid":1667993,"uid":227645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"